Madhya Pradesh
Nov 25, 2014
Murder
Description:
			A local court today awarded life imprisonment to a man for killing his wife.

According to prosecution, Sriram Rasingh (40) axed to death his wife Mamta (36) over suspicion of infidelity at Nihad village near here on November 28 last year.

After going through the material on record, District and Sessions Judge R K Shrivastava sentenced Sriram to undergo life imprisonment and also imposed a fine of Rs 200 on him.


